title: #1608 Since When Does Paying For Everything Count For Nothing?
itunes:title: #1608 Since When Does Paying For Everything Count For Nothing?
description:
Adam and Dr. Drew open the show discussing education and how the process changes as one ages and how you can shift to be effective in a different way as you get older. They also speak to a variety of callers including one looking for advice as a soon to be first time father and another who wants to thank them for keeping him sane these past few years
